cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the problem of single image rain streak removal. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel density-aware multi-stream densely connected convolutional neural network-based algorithm, which involves deep learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions the use of a new dataset, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
